<p>I have a TreeView like this:</p>  <pre><code>        &lt;TreeView LostFocus="treeView_LostFocus"&gt;             &lt;TreeViewItem Selected="treeViewItem_select"/&gt;         &lt;/TreeView&gt; </code></pre>  <p>it always trigger event <code>treeView_LostFocus</code> first when I select different item in TreeViewItem using <code>treeViewItem_select</code>. How can I do to trigger the lost focus event only when the the <code>TreeView</code> losing focus, not before trigger <code>treeViewItem_select</code>?</p>  <p>ps: make <code>e.Handle = true</code> in the end of <code>treeViewItem_select</code> seems not work.</p>